data.description:
Located in one of Flagstaff's hottest neighborhoods, this stunning 4-bedroom home with a hot tub is in a league of its own. You'll feel the pride of ownership the moment you pull onto the driveway. Inside, custom touches like hardwood floors, upgraded wood cabinetry, and central air make it clear this place is special. The heart of the home is the main living area with its high ceilings, big windows, and cozy stone fireplace. The primary suite on the main level is like a private retreat, with a fancy jetted tub, custom shower, and a walk-in closet you could get lost in.The kitchen is a chef's dream, with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar that's perfect for casual meals. With a flex room off the main entry... use that to create an office or a formal dining room, depending on your needs. Outside, the landscaped yard is a gem, with mature trees and plants that have a timed drip system.

But the real magic happens out back. Step onto the paver patio and enter your own mountain paradise. Enjoy the space to sit outside, enjoy the surroundings with a soothing water feature, and a barbecue setup ready for your next cookout. Don't let this unique property slip through your fingers - come check it out before it's gone!
